<text><body>
<cb:mulu level="1" type="其他">拈古</cb:mulu>
<milestone n="8" unit="juan"/>
<pb n="0049a" ed="J" xml:id="J27.B189.0049a"/>
<lb n="0049a01" ed="J"/><cb:mulu n="8" type="卷"></cb:mulu><cb:juan n="8" fun="open"><cb:jhead>三宜盂禪師語錄卷八</cb:jhead></cb:juan>
<lb n="0049a02" ed="J"/><byline cb:type="editor">住雲門顯聖寺門人淨範編</byline>
<lb n="0049a03" ed="J"/><byline cb:type="other">山陰嗣法弟子祁淨超較訂</byline>
<lb n="0049a04" ed="J"/><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu level="1" type="其他">頌古</cb:mulu><head>頌古</head>
<lb n="0049a05" ed="J"/><cb:div type="orig"><p xml:id="pJ27p0049a0501">世尊初生，雲門太平。</p></cb:div>
<lb n="0049a06" ed="J"/><cb:div type="commentary"><p xml:id="pJ27p0049a0601" style="margin-left:1em">韓侯開國<note n="0049a0601" resp="CBETA" type="add">已【CB】，巳【嘉興】</note><app n="0049a0601"><lem resp="CBETA.maha" wit="【CB】">已</lem><rdg wit="【嘉興】">巳</rdg></app>多謀，豈憶邦寧將不留？堪笑雲門誠
<lb n="0049a07" ed="J"/>厚面，自添脂粉不知羞。</p></cb:div>
<lb n="0049a08" ed="J"/><cb:div type="orig"><p xml:id="pJ27p0049a0801">世尊拈華，迦葉微笑。</p></cb:div>
<lb n="0049a09" ed="J"/><cb:div type="commentary"><p xml:id="pJ27p0049a0901" style="margin-left:1em">杜鵑飛入春園裏，穩蹋華枝零碎語。林間驚起昔
<lb n="0049a10" ed="J"/>愁人眼看華枝淚如許。最難舉，東土西天驟紅雨。</p></cb:div>
<lb n="0049a11" ed="J"/><cb:div type="orig"><p xml:id="pJ27p0049a1101">五通仙人問那一通？</p></cb:div>
<lb n="0049a12" ed="J"/><cb:div type="commentary"><p xml:id="pJ27p0049a1201" style="margin-left:1em">那一通，你問我，猢猻上樹偷生果。滿口嚼得不甘
<lb n="0049a13" ed="J"/>香。眼裏耳裏都是火。忽然撞著看。園翁沒處躲。</p></cb:div>
<lb n="0049a14" ed="J"/><cb:div type="orig"><p xml:id="pJ27p0049a1401">女子出定。</p></cb:div>
<lb n="0049a15" ed="J"/><cb:div type="commentary"><p xml:id="pJ27p0049a1501" style="margin-left:1em">玄石一醒醉三年，妻兒抱首哭蒼天，饒君題盡招
<lb n="0049a16" ed="J"/>魂賦，落得安閒自在眠。文殊智，罔明賢，出入如何
<lb n="0049a17" ed="J"/>得話圓？春光不改東風面，惹得江南啼杜鵑。</p></cb:div>
<lb n="0049a18" ed="J"/><cb:div type="orig"><p xml:id="pJ27p0049a1801">金剛經以今世人輕賤三句。</p></cb:div>
<lb n="0049a19" ed="J"/><cb:div type="commentary"><p xml:id="pJ27p0049a1901" style="margin-left:1em">抱璧投秦定國謀，指瑕多為易城羞，歸來不失荊
<lb n="0049a20" ed="J"/>山寶，明月清風滿御樓。</p></cb:div>
<lb n="0049a21" ed="J"/><cb:div type="orig"><p xml:id="pJ27p0049a2101">楞嚴經見、見之時四句：</p></cb:div>
<lb n="0049a22" ed="J"/><cb:div type="commentary"><p xml:id="pJ27p0049a2201" style="margin-left:1em">九里松風天竺路，十洲月上珊瑚枝，此來山水連
<lb n="0049a23" ed="J"/>天碧，正是吳江楓落時。急著眼，莫差池，此事如何
<lb n="0049a24" ed="J"/>說與知？玉鷺飛歸蘆荻渚，芙蓉寂寞秋光遲。</p></cb:div>
<lb n="0049a25" ed="J"/><cb:div type="orig"><p xml:id="pJ27p0049a2501">聖女三般物。</p></cb:div>
<lb n="0049a26" ed="J"/><cb:div type="commentary"><p xml:id="pJ27p0049a2601" style="margin-left:1em">髑髏遍野實堪嗟，拈著無端變作蛇，能是女郎機
<lb n="0049a27" ed="J"/>更捷，解從石上插成華。</p></cb:div>
<lb n="0049a28" ed="J"/><cb:div type="orig"><p xml:id="pJ27p0049a2801">殃崛尊者救產難，</p></cb:div>
<lb n="0049a29" ed="J"/><cb:div type="commentary"><p xml:id="pJ27p0049a2901" style="margin-left:1em">廚下嫂堂上姑不是家親，誰敢相呼？平心等視，失
<lb n="0049a30" ed="J"/>卻宗圖。咄！莫謂六橋花爛熳，須知春色滿皇都。</p>
<pb n="0049b" ed="J" xml:id="J27.B189.0049b"/>
<lb n="0049b01" ed="J"/><p xml:id="pJ27p0049b0101" style="margin-left:1em">冰挾蝦蟆，火飛蝴蜨，柳絮愁霜，荷花愛雪。要得燕
<lb n="0049b02" ed="J"/>國寧太子入秦質。</p>
<lb n="0049b03" ed="J"/><p xml:id="pJ27p0049b0301" style="margin-left:1em">去年今日此門中，人面桃花相映紅，人面不知何
<lb n="0049b04" ed="J"/>處去，桃花依舊笑春風。</p></cb:div>
<lb n="0049b05" ed="J"/><cb:div type="orig"><p xml:id="pJ27p0049b0501">六祖風旛、雪峰與棒。</p></cb:div>
<lb n="0049b06" ed="J"/><cb:div type="commentary"><p xml:id="pJ27p0049b0601" style="margin-left:1em">一點私情奈得羞，也曾漏泄在君侯，病軀正值春
<lb n="0049b07" ed="J"/>三月，華落華開總是愁。</p></cb:div>
<lb n="0049b08" ed="J"/><cb:div type="orig"><p xml:id="pJ27p0049b0801">一祖安心。</p></cb:div>
<lb n="0049b09" ed="J"/><cb:div type="commentary"><p xml:id="pJ27p0049b0901" style="margin-left:1em">教子番成不克家，無端清眼見空華。當時若不來
<lb n="0049b10" ed="J"/>茲土，連璧如何得有瑕？</p></cb:div>
<lb n="0049b11" ed="J"/><cb:div type="orig"><p xml:id="pJ27p0049b1101">國師無縫塔，</p></cb:div>
<lb n="0049b12" ed="J"/><cb:div type="commentary"><p xml:id="pJ27p0049b1201" style="margin-left:1em">月照蘆華，霜風凜冽。漁歌一曲滄浪裏，芙蓉秋老
<lb n="0049b13" ed="J"/>寒江側。</p></cb:div>
<lb n="0049b14" ed="J"/><cb:div type="orig"><p xml:id="pJ27p0049b1401">洞山寒暑，</p></cb:div>
<lb n="0049b15" ed="J"/><cb:div type="commentary"><p xml:id="pJ27p0049b1501" style="margin-left:1em">畫閣鐘沈隔亮紗，梧桐微映月痕邪。海棠春暮成
<lb n="0049b16" ed="J"/>狼藉，風打停舟起浪華。</p></cb:div>
<lb n="0049b17" ed="J"/><cb:div type="orig"><p xml:id="pJ27p0049b1701">經首<unclear></unclear>字。</p></cb:div>
<lb n="0049b18" ed="J"/><cb:div type="commentary"><p xml:id="pJ27p0049b1801" style="margin-left:1em">以字不成，八字不就，乍看是豈細讀？如豆不若兩，
<lb n="0049b19" ed="J"/>宜剜襟續袖。</p></cb:div>
<lb n="0049b20" ed="J"/><cb:div type="orig"><p xml:id="pJ27p0049b2001">德山托缽，巖頭末後。</p></cb:div>
<lb n="0049b21" ed="J"/><cb:div type="commentary"><p xml:id="pJ27p0049b2101" style="margin-left:1em">榴花紅似火，芙蕖飄暗香，夜來風雨後，零落滿池
<lb n="0049b22" ed="J"/>塘。三年活甚參！商令人錯憶修文郎。</p></cb:div>
<lb n="0049b23" ed="J"/><cb:div type="orig"><p xml:id="pJ27p0049b2301">洞山麻三斤。</p></cb:div>
<lb n="0049b24" ed="J"/><cb:div type="commentary"><p xml:id="pJ27p0049b2401" style="margin-left:1em">龍鱗獨角碧麒麟，火眼流光若電新，金鎖玉欄留
<lb n="0049b25" ed="J"/>不住，夜來飛上紫霄宸。</p>
<lb n="0049b26" ed="J"/><p xml:id="pJ27p0049b2601" style="margin-left:1em">敲空有聲，擊木無響，喘月吳牛，得珠象罔。不必如
<lb n="0049b27" ed="J"/>之若何，豈用心思意想。直底直似彎弓曲底，曲如
<lb n="0049b28" ed="J"/>秤幹棒打石人頭嚗嚗短倖底安能漏網。</p></cb:div>
<lb n="0049b29" ed="J"/><cb:div type="orig"><p xml:id="pJ27p0049b2901">興化擯維那。</p></cb:div>
<lb n="0049b30" ed="J"/><cb:div type="commentary"><p xml:id="pJ27p0049b3001" style="margin-left:1em">蒼天！蒼天長底搆，不著短底探過肩，漢王滴淚斬
<pb n="0049c" ed="J" xml:id="J27.B189.0049c"/>
<lb n="0049c01" ed="J"/>丁公。東方朔，割肉而傷廉。王彥方德被鄉井，感得
<lb n="0049c02" ed="J"/>盜牛人守劍之虔。</p></cb:div>
<lb n="0049c03" ed="J"/><cb:div type="orig"><p xml:id="pJ27p0049c0301">趙州勘婆子。</p></cb:div>
<lb n="0049c04" ed="J"/><cb:div type="commentary"><p xml:id="pJ27p0049c0401" style="margin-left:1em">趙州勘破婆羲之好養鵝白毛浮綠，水紅掌撥清
<lb n="0049c05" ed="J"/>波。</p></cb:div>
<lb n="0049c06" ed="J"/><cb:div type="orig"><p xml:id="pJ27p0049c0601">百丈野狐，黃蘗赤鬚。</p></cb:div>
<lb n="0049c07" ed="J"/><cb:div type="commentary"><p xml:id="pJ27p0049c0701" style="margin-left:1em">黃連性苦，甘艸性甜，不落不昧，窮漢賭錢。贏得五
<lb n="0049c08" ed="J"/>百輸了一千。岳陽樓上春風煖，為看桃花自卷簾。
<lb n="0049c09" ed="J"/>不向驪龍求夜光，野狐之說成商量。可憐一段天
<lb n="0049c10" ed="J"/>機錦，裂碎人間作小裳。落不落，昧不昧，春風一曲
<lb n="0049c11" ed="J"/>薔薇醉。</p></cb:div>
<lb n="0049c12" ed="J"/><cb:div type="orig"><p xml:id="pJ27p0049c1201">溈山、仰山摘茶體用。</p></cb:div>
<lb n="0049c13" ed="J"/><cb:div type="commentary"><p xml:id="pJ27p0049c1301" style="margin-left:1em">只得用不得體沙裏無油卻有水，只得體不得用。
<lb n="0049c14" ed="J"/>龜毛拂子三斤重放子三十棒呵呵呵衣羅孃子
<lb n="0049c15" ed="J"/>自言俏。三度下堂呼婢子。</p></cb:div>
<lb n="0049c16" ed="J"/><cb:div type="orig"><p xml:id="pJ27p0049c1601">國師三喚侍者。</p></cb:div>
<lb n="0049c17" ed="J"/><cb:div type="commentary"><p xml:id="pJ27p0049c1701" style="margin-left:1em">端陽解粽，中秋步月，不是好事，應箇時節。彭祖奇
<lb n="0049c18" ed="J"/>壽八百歲，有話不對妻兒說：</p>
<lb n="0049c19" ed="J"/><p xml:id="pJ27p0049c1901" style="margin-left:1em">三、呼侍者弄巧成拙，侍者三應自失一橛，天上月
<lb n="0049c20" ed="J"/>圜，人間半月，有恩難報，朝提暮挈。復云：咄！</p></cb:div>
<lb n="0049c21" ed="J"/><cb:div type="orig"><p xml:id="pJ27p0049c2101">趙州鬥劣不鬥勝。</p></cb:div>
<lb n="0049c22" ed="J"/><cb:div type="commentary"><p xml:id="pJ27p0049c2201" style="margin-left:1em">得便宜底，常帶羞贏，官司底常叫屈，為甚如此？小
<lb n="0049c23" ed="J"/>雪見雪囤米底折一橛。</p></cb:div>
<lb n="0049c24" ed="J"/><cb:div type="orig"><p xml:id="pJ27p0049c2401">黃龍三關。</p></cb:div>
<lb n="0049c25" ed="J"/><cb:div type="commentary"><p xml:id="pJ27p0049c2501" style="margin-left:1em">我手何似佛手，鼻頭底下是口？若不是王老師機
<lb n="0049c26" ed="J"/>關險些兒證貓成狗。</p>
<lb n="0049c27" ed="J"/><p xml:id="pJ27p0049c2701" style="margin-left:1em">我腳何似驢腳海？龍王昨夜惡發連下了，三日三
<lb n="0049c28" ed="J"/>夜石，烏龜幾希曬殺！</p>
<lb n="0049c29" ed="J"/><p xml:id="pJ27p0049c2901" style="margin-left:1em">人人有箇生緣，不是花邊是柳邊。呂洞賓岳陽三
<lb n="0049c30" ed="J"/>醉張，果老騎驢上天。</p></cb:div>
<pb n="0050a" ed="J" xml:id="J27.B189.0050a"/>
<lb n="0050a01" ed="J"/><cb:div type="orig"><p xml:id="pJ27p0050a0101">靈雲見桃花悟道。</p></cb:div>
<lb n="0050a02" ed="J"/><cb:div type="commentary"><p xml:id="pJ27p0050a0201" style="margin-left:1em">一分春色一分華，卻笑靈雲眼翳沙。假若鄙夫無
<lb n="0050a03" ed="J"/>識見，定知田服是僧家。復斫額云：<g ref="#CB01403"/>。</p></cb:div>
<lb n="0050a04" ed="J"/><cb:div type="orig"><p xml:id="pJ27p0050a0401">子湖狗。</p></cb:div>
<lb n="0050a05" ed="J"/><cb:div type="commentary"><p xml:id="pJ27p0050a0501" style="margin-left:1em">子湖狗竹響，風過便哮，吼取人心，取人首，衲子望
<lb n="0050a06" ed="J"/>崖俱卻走。縱使當時不渡江，也被攔胸傷一口。為
<lb n="0050a07" ed="J"/>甚如此？駿獒原，不受人驅，司夜韓盧隨處有。</p></cb:div>
<lb n="0050a08" ed="J"/><cb:div type="orig"><p xml:id="pJ27p0050a0801">趙州佛性有無。</p></cb:div>
<lb n="0050a09" ed="J"/><cb:div type="commentary"><p xml:id="pJ27p0050a0901" style="margin-left:1em">狗子有賣扇，老婆日遮手。狗子無種瓢，先得喫胡
<lb n="0050a10" ed="J"/>盧。天稟原來各不同，盧仝不飲劉伶酒。</p></cb:div>
<lb n="0050a11" ed="J"/><cb:div type="orig"><p xml:id="pJ27p0050a1101">乾峰舉一雲門出眾，</p></cb:div>
<lb n="0050a12" ed="J"/><cb:div type="commentary"><p xml:id="pJ27p0050a1201" style="margin-left:1em">桃如是紅，李如是白，雖則各無言，一一依時節。鳥
<lb n="0050a13" ed="J"/>飛空而無蹤，魚行水而不轍，非因緣之他宗，非自
<lb n="0050a14" ed="J"/>然之邪說。問取露柱燈籠，有口兩難分別。</p></cb:div>
<lb n="0050a15" ed="J"/><cb:div type="orig"><p xml:id="pJ27p0050a1501">疏山造塔，羅山著語。</p></cb:div>
<lb n="0050a16" ed="J"/><cb:div type="commentary"><p xml:id="pJ27p0050a1601" style="margin-left:1em">一文錢紛紛，葉落正秋天。兩文錢水光，山色楚江
<lb n="0050a17" ed="J"/>邊。三文錢杏花，如雨柳拖煙。不若南陽無縫塔，官
<lb n="0050a18" ed="J"/>家親為發工錢。至今獨鎮乾輿裏，山海悠悠月自
<lb n="0050a19" ed="J"/>圜。</p></cb:div>
<lb n="0050a20" ed="J"/><cb:div type="orig"><p xml:id="pJ27p0050a2001">船子接夾山，</p></cb:div>
<lb n="0050a21" ed="J"/><cb:div type="commentary"><p xml:id="pJ27p0050a2101" style="margin-left:1em">靈龜抴尾跡偏賒，挂角羚羊事可嗟，不若石人騎
<lb n="0050a22" ed="J"/>木馬，臨宵解轡早歸家。</p></cb:div>
<lb n="0050a23" ed="J"/><cb:div type="orig"><p xml:id="pJ27p0050a2301">夾山接洛浦，</p></cb:div>
<lb n="0050a24" ed="J"/><cb:div type="commentary"><p xml:id="pJ27p0050a2401" style="margin-left:1em">沈香亭下醉題詩，寵辱相憐在一時，雲月谿山同
<lb n="0050a25" ed="J"/>有異，終身落魄夜郎西。</p></cb:div>
<lb n="0050a26" ed="J"/><cb:div type="orig"><p xml:id="pJ27p0050a2601">臨濟喫棒，悟後還掌。</p></cb:div>
<lb n="0050a27" ed="J"/><cb:div type="commentary"><p xml:id="pJ27p0050a2701" style="margin-left:1em">冶城鞴銕沖牛斗，黃檗偏遭霹靂手。掀翻滄海蹴
<lb n="0050a28" ed="J"/>須彌，陣衄脩羅俱北走。兒孫從此說家風，羅剎江
<lb n="0050a29" ed="J"/>聲日夜吼。</p></cb:div>
<lb n="0050a30" ed="J"/><cb:div type="orig"><p xml:id="pJ27p0050a3001">金剛寶劍。</p></cb:div>
<pb n="0050b" ed="J" xml:id="J27.B189.0050b"/>
<lb n="0050b01" ed="J"/><cb:div type="commentary"><p xml:id="pJ27p0050b0101" style="margin-left:1em">出鞘龍泉覿面揮，臨機正令壯軍威。徒勞擬思難
<lb n="0050b02" ed="J"/>迴互，腥血從茲濺衲衣。</p></cb:div>
<lb n="0050b03" ed="J"/><cb:div type="orig"><p xml:id="pJ27p0050b0301">踞地獅子。</p></cb:div>
<lb n="0050b04" ed="J"/><cb:div type="commentary"><p xml:id="pJ27p0050b0401" style="margin-left:1em">鋒牙利爪踞崖前，疊嶂春風華木鮮，香象且無棲
<lb n="0050b05" ed="J"/>泊地，野狐何事得躋緣？</p></cb:div>
<lb n="0050b06" ed="J"/><cb:div type="orig"><p xml:id="pJ27p0050b0601">探竿影艸，</p></cb:div>
<lb n="0050b07" ed="J"/><cb:div type="commentary"><p xml:id="pJ27p0050b0701" style="margin-left:1em">水滿平湖月滿川，梢人難自定風煙。要知入海堪
<lb n="0050b08" ed="J"/>行候，且看雲飛出渡前。咄！請下一轉語。</p></cb:div>
<lb n="0050b09" ed="J"/><cb:div type="orig"><p xml:id="pJ27p0050b0901">一喝不作一喝用。</p></cb:div>
<lb n="0050b10" ed="J"/><cb:div type="commentary"><p xml:id="pJ27p0050b1001" style="margin-left:1em">電捲星馳難側轉，穿鍼石火休遲眼，吹簫人在畫
<lb n="0050b11" ed="J"/>樓中，華落鶯啼水清淺。</p></cb:div>
<lb n="0050b12" ed="J"/><cb:div type="orig"><p xml:id="pJ27p0050b1201">婆子轉藏。</p></cb:div>
<lb n="0050b13" ed="J"/><cb:div type="commentary"><p xml:id="pJ27p0050b1301" style="margin-left:1em">轉全藏初三月挂梅枝上轉，半藏春光，深入蕉心
<lb n="0050b14" ed="J"/>放<note n="0050b1401" resp="CBETA" type="add" note_key="J27.0050b14.02">妺【CB】，妹【嘉興】（CBETA 按：可參考《佩觿》卷下第38頁：「妹妺，上莫佩翻姉妹，下音末桀妻。」）</note><app n="0050b1401"><lem wit="【CB】" resp="CBETA.ting">妺</lem><rdg wit="【嘉興】">妹</rdg></app>嬉尤物能亡國僊子脩丹在蓬閬，要得公案
<lb n="0050b15" ed="J"/>圜臭鶻臀揮三十棒。</p></cb:div>
<lb n="0050b16" ed="J"/><cb:div type="orig"><p xml:id="pJ27p0050b1601">香嚴擊竹，仰山親勘。</p></cb:div>
<lb n="0050b17" ed="J"/><cb:div type="commentary"><p xml:id="pJ27p0050b1701" style="margin-left:1em">悟在從緣得最親，也勝紙墨遠求人，從茲一擊清
<lb n="0050b18" ed="J"/>風起，翠影蕭蕭抴四鄰。</p></cb:div>
<lb n="0050b19" ed="J"/><cb:div type="orig"><p xml:id="pJ27p0050b1901">雲門須彌山，</p></cb:div>
<lb n="0050b20" ed="J"/><cb:div type="commentary"><p xml:id="pJ27p0050b2001" style="margin-left:1em">須彌山，南州之北，北州南腰躔日月天在頂，李四
<lb n="0050b21" ed="J"/>不識問張三洞庭，湖闊連天塹。秋深水色湛如藍
<lb n="0050b22" ed="J"/>鼓山箭折。</p>
<lb n="0050b23" ed="J"/><p xml:id="pJ27p0050b2301" style="margin-left:1em">奪路臨機自得宜，寧知出馬被人嗤？縱然箭折歸
<lb n="0050b24" ed="J"/>城去，不受軍師暗裏欺。凍儂老有鄉情，黃河千載
<lb n="0050b25" ed="J"/>一時清。果然豹有吞孃志，兩箇黃鸝一樣聲。</p></cb:div>
<lb n="0050b26" ed="J"/><cb:div type="orig"><p xml:id="pJ27p0050b2601">瑞巖主人公，</p></cb:div>
<lb n="0050b27" ed="J"/><cb:div type="commentary"><p xml:id="pJ27p0050b2701" style="margin-left:1em">瑞巖老翁喚主人公，一聲霹靂打死雷公。</p></cb:div>
<lb n="0050b28" ed="J"/><cb:div type="orig"><p xml:id="pJ27p0050b2801">玄沙因我得禮汝。</p></cb:div>
<lb n="0050b29" ed="J"/><cb:div type="commentary"><p xml:id="pJ27p0050b2901" style="margin-left:1em">因我你得禮，對鏡勤梳洗，一箇搽臙脂，二人紅卻
<lb n="0050b30" ed="J"/>觜。</p></cb:div>
<pb n="0050c" ed="J" xml:id="J27.B189.0050c"/>
<lb n="0050c01" ed="J"/><cb:div type="orig"><p xml:id="pJ27p0050c0101">寰中大慈禪師云：山僧不解畣話，秖能識病。時有僧
<lb n="0050c02" ed="J"/>出，師便歸方丈。</p></cb:div>
<lb n="0050c03" ed="J"/><cb:div type="commentary"><p xml:id="pJ27p0050c0301" style="margin-left:1em">霜摧秋葉滿秋山，古路無人鳥自還，出谷白雲飛
<lb n="0050c04" ed="J"/>不定，數行征雁影斑斑。</p></cb:div>
<lb n="0050c05" ed="J"/><cb:div type="orig"><p xml:id="pJ27p0050c0501">趙州勘二菴主。</p></cb:div>
<lb n="0050c06" ed="J"/><cb:div type="commentary"><p xml:id="pJ27p0050c0601" style="margin-left:1em">有口難言不共讎，趙州陸地善行舟，嚴陵豈肯從
<lb n="0050c07" ed="J"/>君命，穩坐瀟湘明月樓。</p></cb:div>
<lb n="0050c08" ed="J"/><cb:div type="orig"><p xml:id="pJ27p0050c0801">趙州云：佛之一字，吾不喜聞。</p></cb:div>
<lb n="0050c09" ed="J"/><cb:div type="commentary"><p xml:id="pJ27p0050c0901" style="margin-left:1em">佛之一字不喜聞，長安爭看狀元新，金花親賜金
<lb n="0050c10" ed="J"/>鑾殿，不是當時窗下人。恩可酬怨難申，面南率土
<lb n="0050c11" ed="J"/>皆王土，易姓良臣便不臣。</p></cb:div>
<lb n="0050c12" ed="J"/><cb:div type="orig"><p xml:id="pJ27p0050c1201">黃檗坐南泉位，</p></cb:div>
<lb n="0050c13" ed="J"/><cb:div type="commentary"><p xml:id="pJ27p0050c1301" style="margin-left:1em">陷虎之機，當仁不讓，可惜王老師，輸卻無頭狀。</p></cb:div>
<lb n="0050c14" ed="J"/><cb:div type="orig"><p xml:id="pJ27p0050c1401">鹽官犀牛扇子。</p></cb:div>
<lb n="0050c15" ed="J"/><cb:div type="commentary"><p xml:id="pJ27p0050c1501" style="margin-left:1em">扇破之言卻好酬，如何詰著便亡牛？鹽官只為婆
<lb n="0050c16" ed="J"/>心切，彼此都成第二頭。</p></cb:div>
<lb n="0050c17" ed="J"/><cb:div type="orig"><p xml:id="pJ27p0050c1701">東寺示眾曰：心不是佛，智不是道。劍去遠矣，爾方刻
<lb n="0050c18" ed="J"/>舟。</p></cb:div>
<lb n="0050c19" ed="J"/><cb:div type="commentary"><p xml:id="pJ27p0050c1901" style="margin-left:1em">水村山郭自成家，前後紅黃四序花，漁舟傍晚不
<lb n="0050c20" ed="J"/>歸去，深樹高棲亂乳鴉。</p></cb:div>
<lb n="0050c21" ed="J"/><cb:div type="orig"><p xml:id="pJ27p0050c2101">西園曇藏禪師，一日自燒浴次，僧問：何不使沙彌園
<lb n="0050c22" ed="J"/>拊掌三下？</p></cb:div>
<lb n="0050c23" ed="J"/><cb:div type="commentary"><p xml:id="pJ27p0050c2301" style="margin-left:1em">尋得桃源好避秦，桃花又見一年春，花飛<note n="0050c2301" resp="CBETA" type="add">已【CB】，巳【嘉興】</note><app n="0050c2301"><lem resp="CBETA.maha" wit="【CB】">已</lem><rdg wit="【嘉興】">巳</rdg></app>是隨
<lb n="0050c24" ed="J"/>流水，引得漁郎來問津。</p></cb:div>
<lb n="0050c25" ed="J"/><cb:div type="orig"><p xml:id="pJ27p0050c2501">金牛舞飯。</p></cb:div>
<lb n="0050c26" ed="J"/><cb:div type="commentary"><p xml:id="pJ27p0050c2601" style="margin-left:1em">龍得水時添意氣，虎逢山勢長威獰，黃河盡有通
<lb n="0050c27" ed="J"/>天路，不是其人不敢行。</p></cb:div>
<lb n="0050c28" ed="J"/><cb:div type="orig"><p xml:id="pJ27p0050c2801">浮杯和尚凌行婆來參<note place="inline">至</note>為人即禍生。</p></cb:div>
<lb n="0050c29" ed="J"/><cb:div type="commentary"><p xml:id="pJ27p0050c2901" style="margin-left:1em">覿面之機，作家頗愛；失之豪氂，汞飛爐內。</p></cb:div>
<lb n="0050c30" ed="J"/><cb:div type="orig"><p xml:id="pJ27p0050c3001">後有僧傳至南泉<note place="inline">至</note>伎死禪和，如麻似粟。</p></cb:div>
<pb n="0051a" ed="J" xml:id="J27.B189.0051a"/>
<lb n="0051a01" ed="J"/><cb:div type="commentary"><p xml:id="pJ27p0051a0101" style="margin-left:1em">靈龜負圖，兩彩一賽，可悲可痛，失錢遭罪。</p></cb:div>
<lb n="0051a02" ed="J"/><cb:div type="orig"><p xml:id="pJ27p0051a0201">一、舉似趙州<note place="inline">至</note>幾喪目前機。</p></cb:div>
<lb n="0051a03" ed="J"/><cb:div type="commentary"><p xml:id="pJ27p0051a0301" style="margin-left:1em">拈得黃金，變成土塊，碧琉璃缾，一錘擊碎。雖然坦
<lb n="0051a04" ed="J"/>途，好生險隘。</p></cb:div>
<lb n="0051a05" ed="J"/><cb:div type="orig"><p xml:id="pJ27p0051a0501">道吾雲巖，一榮一枯。</p></cb:div>
<lb n="0051a06" ed="J"/><cb:div type="commentary"><p xml:id="pJ27p0051a0601" style="margin-left:1em">雲巖春色滿皇都，葉落根枯是道吾。還有春秋俱
<lb n="0051a07" ed="J"/>不涉，洞賓腰挂藥胡盧。</p></cb:div>
<lb n="0051a08" ed="J"/><cb:div type="orig"><p xml:id="pJ27p0051a0801">丹霞燒木佛，院主墮眉鬚。</p></cb:div>
<lb n="0051a09" ed="J"/><cb:div type="commentary"><p xml:id="pJ27p0051a0901" style="margin-left:1em">丹霞火浴三千佛，院主眉藏五老峰，莫道是非難
<lb n="0051a10" ed="J"/>辯別，有錢何處不春風？</p></cb:div>
<lb n="0051a11" ed="J"/><cb:div type="orig"><p xml:id="pJ27p0051a1101">大顛擯首座。</p></cb:div>
<lb n="0051a12" ed="J"/><cb:div type="commentary"><p xml:id="pJ27p0051a1201" style="margin-left:1em">一樣酬機動齒齗，生緣難說共青春，雷同若是登
<lb n="0051a13" ed="J"/>金榜，誤殺英雄沒量人。</p></cb:div>
<lb n="0051a14" ed="J"/><cb:div type="orig"><p xml:id="pJ27p0051a1401">一、釋迦、二元和，三佛陀。自餘是甚麼碗躂丘。</p></cb:div>
<lb n="0051a15" ed="J"/><cb:div type="commentary"><p xml:id="pJ27p0051a1501" style="margin-left:1em">釋迦元和與佛陀、摩訶<g ref="#CB02739"/>達哩娑訶，自餘甚麼碗
<lb n="0051a16" ed="J"/>躂丘六。一居士歐陽修，三山半落青天外，二水中
<lb n="0051a17" ed="J"/>分白鷺洲。</p></cb:div>
<lb n="0051a18" ed="J"/><cb:div type="orig"><p xml:id="pJ27p0051a1801">百丈併卻咽喉脣吻。</p></cb:div>
<lb n="0051a19" ed="J"/><cb:div type="commentary"><p xml:id="pJ27p0051a1901" style="margin-left:1em">卻請和尚道：野火燒神，離古廟折角，泥牛飛過山
<lb n="0051a20" ed="J"/>風，卷波濤雲渺渺。和尚也須併卻，大雪紛紛正飄
<lb n="0051a21" ed="J"/>攃。藍關欲度馬難行，雲裏僊人綰ㄚ角。和尚有也
<lb n="0051a22" ed="J"/>未？泥塑天王打瞌睡。寒山拾得笑歸來，兩腳何曾
<lb n="0051a23" ed="J"/>蹋著地。</p></cb:div>
<lb n="0051a24" ed="J"/><cb:div type="orig"><p xml:id="pJ27p0051a2401">人梅鼠聲。</p></cb:div>
<lb n="0051a25" ed="J"/><cb:div type="commentary"><p xml:id="pJ27p0051a2501" style="margin-left:1em">即此物非他物，杜鵑啼出猩猩血，行人錯認柳梢
<lb n="0051a26" ed="J"/>頭，春城幾箇知時節。山有谷而藏雲，水有淵而含
<lb n="0051a27" ed="J"/>月。家家地上可栽松，一任枝枝與葉葉。</p></cb:div>
<lb n="0051a28" ed="J"/><cb:div type="orig"><p xml:id="pJ27p0051a2801">南泉斬貓，趙州頂鞋。</p></cb:div>
<lb n="0051a29" ed="J"/><cb:div type="commentary"><p xml:id="pJ27p0051a2901" style="margin-left:1em">南泉有擎山之手，趙州有掬海之能。令嚴則佛祖
<lb n="0051a30" ed="J"/>攢眉，法正則四海準繩。分明白日昭昭也，多少愁
<pb n="0051b" ed="J" xml:id="J27.B189.0051b"/>
<lb n="0051b01" ed="J"/>人暗裏行。</p>
<lb n="0051b02" ed="J"/><p xml:id="pJ27p0051b0201" style="margin-left:1em">刀頭有物甜如蜜，玅在善嘗不割舌，趙老曾不動
<lb n="0051b03" ed="J"/>鋒芒，爛嚼秋江一片月。</p></cb:div>
<lb n="0051b04" ed="J"/><cb:div type="orig"><p xml:id="pJ27p0051b0401">三世諸佛不知有，黧奴白牯卻知有。</p></cb:div>
<lb n="0051b05" ed="J"/><cb:div type="commentary"><p xml:id="pJ27p0051b0501" style="margin-left:1em">三世諸佛不知有，自甘落魄沽清酒，終日昏昏不
<lb n="0051b06" ed="J"/>舉頭，猢猻海底翻筋斗。黧奴白牯卻知有，指揮日
<lb n="0051b07" ed="J"/>月朝東走，端的難謾王老師，癩豬生得子湖狗。</p></cb:div>
<lb n="0051b08" ed="J"/><cb:div type="orig"><p xml:id="pJ27p0051b0801">香嚴獨腳頌，</p></cb:div>
<lb n="0051b09" ed="J"/><cb:div type="commentary"><p xml:id="pJ27p0051b0901" style="margin-left:1em">子啐母啄易，子母兩亡難，夜來霜重蘆枝折，鷺鷥
<lb n="0051b10" ed="J"/>對對出沙灘。</p></cb:div>
<lb n="0051b11" ed="J"/><cb:div type="orig"><p xml:id="pJ27p0051b1101">鐘樓上唱贊床腳下種菜。</p></cb:div>
<lb n="0051b12" ed="J"/><cb:div type="commentary"><p xml:id="pJ27p0051b1201" style="margin-left:1em">十字街頭石，敢當離家日久卻思鄉鱸魚畢竟江
<lb n="0051b13" ed="J"/>南美，蓴葉浮波橘正黃。</p></cb:div>
<lb n="0051b14" ed="J"/><cb:div type="orig"><p xml:id="pJ27p0051b1401">漸源覓靈骨。</p></cb:div>
<lb n="0051b15" ed="J"/><cb:div type="commentary"><p xml:id="pJ27p0051b1501" style="margin-left:1em">敗子當時不做家，卻來洪浪汰金沙。犀因翫月紋
<lb n="0051b16" ed="J"/>生角，象被雷驚華入牙。鍼劄不入何處覓？銕鎚煮
<lb n="0051b17" ed="J"/>出黃金汁。秦皇暴虐好焚書，土壁泥牆幸收得。</p></cb:div>
<lb n="0051b18" ed="J"/><cb:div type="orig"><p xml:id="pJ27p0051b1801">大死卻活，侯黑侯白。</p></cb:div>
<lb n="0051b19" ed="J"/><cb:div type="commentary"><p xml:id="pJ27p0051b1901" style="margin-left:1em">此事誰言調不同？原來到處有春風。作家彼此皆
<lb n="0051b20" ed="J"/>堪賞，竹杖投陂化作龍。識藥忌，正宗風，可知版蕩
<lb n="0051b21" ed="J"/>出英雄。</p></cb:div>
<lb n="0051b22" ed="J"/><cb:div type="orig"><p xml:id="pJ27p0051b2201">興化打中間。</p></cb:div>
<lb n="0051b23" ed="J"/><cb:div type="commentary"><p xml:id="pJ27p0051b2301" style="margin-left:1em">古廟裏堪避雨，白日休言曾見鬼。柳條芳艸一時
<lb n="0051b24" ed="J"/>新。池塘香透荷華蕊。</p></cb:div>
<lb n="0051b25" ed="J"/><cb:div type="orig"><p xml:id="pJ27p0051b2501">桐峰大蟲。</p></cb:div>
<lb n="0051b26" ed="J"/><cb:div type="commentary"><p xml:id="pJ27p0051b2601" style="margin-left:1em">山裏大蟲山裏吼。借你拳頭築你口。丈夫氣寓信
<lb n="0051b27" ed="J"/>如王。豈肯輸人甘落後。賊賊賊喜底是。風怨底是
<lb n="0051b28" ed="J"/>雪。</p></cb:div>
<lb n="0051b29" ed="J"/><cb:div type="orig"><p xml:id="pJ27p0051b2901">巖頭四藏鋒，一就事藏鋒。</p></cb:div>
<lb n="0051b30" ed="J"/><cb:div type="commentary"><p xml:id="pJ27p0051b3001" style="margin-left:1em">就事藏鋒理不詮，秖於事上用綿綿，黃鸝不為貪
<pb n="0051c" ed="J" xml:id="J27.B189.0051c"/>
<lb n="0051c01" ed="J"/>華住，飛入橋西楊柳煙。</p></cb:div>
<lb n="0051c02" ed="J"/><cb:div type="orig"><p xml:id="pJ27p0051c0201">二、就理。</p></cb:div>
<lb n="0051c03" ed="J"/><cb:div type="commentary"><p xml:id="pJ27p0051c0301" style="margin-left:1em">就理藏鋒理最真，晴空無地著纖塵，鷺鷥夜宿蘆
<lb n="0051c04" ed="J"/>華裏，秋水秋光一色新。</p></cb:div>
<lb n="0051c05" ed="J"/><cb:div type="orig"><p xml:id="pJ27p0051c0501">三、入就。</p></cb:div>
<lb n="0051c06" ed="J"/><cb:div type="commentary"><p xml:id="pJ27p0051c0601" style="margin-left:1em">入就藏鋒理事全，白雲飛起正晴天，青猿攀折香
<lb n="0051c07" ed="J"/>梨樹，萬水歸江月滿川。</p></cb:div>
<lb n="0051c08" ed="J"/><cb:div type="orig"><p xml:id="pJ27p0051c0801">四、出就。</p></cb:div>
<lb n="0051c09" ed="J"/><cb:div type="commentary"><p xml:id="pJ27p0051c0901" style="margin-left:1em">出就藏鋒事理融，一輪紅日正當空。龍吟虎嘯宣
<lb n="0051c10" ed="J"/>何旨？木馬泥牛調不同。</p></cb:div>
<lb n="0051c11" ed="J"/><cb:div type="orig"><p xml:id="pJ27p0051c1101">雪峰南山鱉鼻蛇，</p></cb:div>
<lb n="0051c12" ed="J"/><cb:div type="commentary"><p xml:id="pJ27p0051c1201" style="margin-left:1em">好條蛇誰解弄？動著驀然生罅縫。長慶老，不惜命，
<lb n="0051c13" ed="J"/>出向人前誇口騁。雲門拄杖似縣弧，玄沙所貴言
<lb n="0051c14" ed="J"/>前定。象骨山高艸最深，如何能得免蛇侵？鋒牙吐
<lb n="0051c15" ed="J"/>毒氣熏天，龍甲金精千百變。學禪翁須子細，十二
<lb n="0051c16" ed="J"/>時中切須避，些些失照便遭傷，鮮血淋漓腥滿地。</p></cb:div>
<lb n="0051c17" ed="J"/><cb:div type="orig"><p xml:id="pJ27p0051c1701">曹山井覷驢。</p></cb:div>
<lb n="0051c18" ed="J"/><cb:div type="commentary"><p xml:id="pJ27p0051c1801" style="margin-left:1em">驢覷井尊中錯認弓蛇影井覷驢滾油鐺裏煮醯
<lb n="0051c19" ed="J"/>雞。兩重公案。一般參莊周蝴蜨。二俱宜春回。是處
<lb n="0051c20" ed="J"/>難藏隱瓊林華發珊瑚支。</p></cb:div>
<lb n="0051c21" ed="J"/><cb:div type="orig"><p xml:id="pJ27p0051c2101">禾山四打鼓，</p></cb:div>
<lb n="0051c22" ed="J"/><cb:div type="commentary"><p xml:id="pJ27p0051c2201" style="margin-left:1em">嵇康精於鍛，馮婦善搏虎，紛紛衲子用心求，爭似
<lb n="0051c23" ed="J"/>禾山解打鼓。君不見有條攀處便攀條黃帝以蹴
<lb n="0051c24" ed="J"/>鞠而練軍武，擬求禪道，佛法高聲云：苦！苦！苦！</p></cb:div>
<lb n="0051c25" ed="J"/><cb:div type="orig"><p xml:id="pJ27p0051c2501">雪峰火焰玄沙王令。</p></cb:div>
<lb n="0051c26" ed="J"/><cb:div type="commentary"><p xml:id="pJ27p0051c2601" style="margin-left:1em">一番提起一番新，續火傳薪用得親，二老欲思重
<lb n="0051c27" ed="J"/>話會，佛前銀燭笑頻頻。阿呵呵！荒田沒人耕，耕動
<lb n="0051c28" ed="J"/>便來爭。</p></cb:div>
<lb n="0051c29" ed="J"/><cb:div type="orig"><p xml:id="pJ27p0051c2901">長慶二種語，保福喫茶去。</p></cb:div>
<lb n="0051c30" ed="J"/><cb:div type="commentary"><p xml:id="pJ27p0051c3001" style="margin-left:1em">如來語無二說稜公何苦？霜加雪兒啼，不止無柰
<pb n="0052a" ed="J" xml:id="J27.B189.0052a"/>
<lb n="0052a01" ed="J"/>何，笑指精金即黃葉二種語。喫茶去，奪得錦袍稱
<lb n="0052a02" ed="J"/>及第。稜公稜公休耳聾，一輪月上海門東。</p></cb:div>
<lb n="0052a03" ed="J"/><cb:div type="orig"><p xml:id="pJ27p0052a0301">雲門對一說，</p></cb:div>
<lb n="0052a04" ed="J"/><cb:div type="commentary"><p xml:id="pJ27p0052a0401" style="margin-left:1em">對一說，較奇絕，白額大蟲新出穴，風行艸偃吼如
<lb n="0052a05" ed="J"/>雷，牛羊不見流鮮血，韶陽老失一橛。</p>
<lb n="0052a06" ed="J"/><p xml:id="pJ27p0052a0601" style="margin-left:1em">玉不雕而有文，空已印而成訣，寶軸盈海藏龍宮，
<lb n="0052a07" ed="J"/>金章與法界齊說。四十九年波翻海口，三百餘會，
<lb n="0052a08" ed="J"/>長空滿月。只為逗教關機，失卻從前一橛對一說，
<lb n="0052a09" ed="J"/>萬里一條銕。</p></cb:div>
<lb n="0052a10" ed="J"/><cb:div type="orig"><p xml:id="pJ27p0052a1001">雲門倒一說。</p></cb:div>
<lb n="0052a11" ed="J"/><cb:div type="commentary"><p xml:id="pJ27p0052a1101" style="margin-left:1em">倒一說，難語決鏤塵析縷重，重說雲起南山雨又
<lb n="0052a12" ed="J"/>來，大抵不是晴時節。白白白梅花，香冷霜天月。</p>
<lb n="0052a13" ed="J"/><p xml:id="pJ27p0052a1301" style="margin-left:1em">雲門倒一說，臨濟白拈賊。虎養豹須防，獅子解反
<lb n="0052a14" ed="J"/><note n="0052a1401" resp="CBETA" type="add">擲【CB】，<g ref="#CB21116"/>【嘉興】</note><app n="0052a1401"><lem resp="CBETA.maha" wit="【CB】">擲</lem><rdg wit="【嘉興】"><g ref="#CB21116"/></rdg></app>，月落潭有聲，花飛侵艸色。柄殺活之威，得權衡
<lb n="0052a15" ed="J"/>之訣。倒一說趯倒繫驢橛。</p></cb:div>
<lb n="0052a16" ed="J"/><cb:div type="orig"><p xml:id="pJ27p0052a1601">雲門六不收。</p></cb:div>
<lb n="0052a17" ed="J"/><cb:div type="commentary"><p xml:id="pJ27p0052a1701" style="margin-left:1em">金木水火土，西天人打鼓，驚動海龍王苦苦苦，水
<lb n="0052a18" ed="J"/>晶宮裏日方午。</p></cb:div>
<lb n="0052a19" ed="J"/><cb:div type="orig"><p xml:id="pJ27p0052a1901">雲門日日好日。</p></cb:div>
<lb n="0052a20" ed="J"/><cb:div type="commentary"><p xml:id="pJ27p0052a2001" style="margin-left:1em">日日是好日，何勞魏闕頒？春曆古今，晷運送春秋。
<lb n="0052a21" ed="J"/>虛空畫出龍蛇跡山蒼蒼水潝潝，西江一口從容
<lb n="0052a22" ed="J"/>吸南高峰瞌睡了一生，錯計小盡無三十。</p></cb:div>
<lb n="0052a23" ed="J"/><cb:div type="orig"><p xml:id="pJ27p0052a2301">雲門顧鑒咦：</p></cb:div>
<lb n="0052a24" ed="J"/><cb:div type="commentary"><p xml:id="pJ27p0052a2401" style="margin-left:1em">已入吾門不再三，祇於顧處越重關，可憐擬議成
<lb n="0052a25" ed="J"/>塗路，要轉靈機直下難。</p></cb:div>
<lb n="0052a26" ed="J"/><cb:div type="orig"><p xml:id="pJ27p0052a2601">法燈西來意，</p></cb:div>
<lb n="0052a27" ed="J"/><cb:div type="commentary"><p xml:id="pJ27p0052a2701" style="margin-left:1em">版齒毛長白醭生，嘮嘮猶說繼傳燈。要知世代金
<lb n="0052a28" ed="J"/>輪子，不受台銜俊髦稱。</p></cb:div>
<lb n="0052a29" ed="J"/><cb:div type="orig"><p xml:id="pJ27p0052a2901">倩女離魂那箇真？</p></cb:div>
<lb n="0052a30" ed="J"/><cb:div type="commentary"><p xml:id="pJ27p0052a3001" style="margin-left:1em">離魂倩女忽還家，堂上相逢不較些。月下錯驚梅
<pb n="0052b" ed="J" xml:id="J27.B189.0052b"/>
<lb n="0052b01" ed="J"/>蕊落，原來上下一枝華。</p></cb:div>
<lb n="0052b02" ed="J"/><cb:div type="orig"><p xml:id="pJ27p0052b0201">玅喜問僧：五祖道：趙州狗子無佛性。也勝貓兒十萬
<lb n="0052b03" ed="J"/>倍。如何？僧云：風行。艸偃喜云：你也不亂道，卻作麼生
<lb n="0052b04" ed="J"/>會？僧無語。喜云：學語之流。便打出。</p></cb:div>
<lb n="0052b05" ed="J"/><cb:div type="commentary"><p xml:id="pJ27p0052b0501" style="margin-left:1em">狗子勝貓十萬倍，金毛獅子艸裏擂。艸偃風行不
<lb n="0052b06" ed="J"/>亂說，玅喜大似白拈賊。學語之流正好打，囌嚕<g ref="#CB02739"/>
<lb n="0052b07" ed="J"/>唎吽泮吒。</p></cb:div>
<lb n="0052b08" ed="J"/><cb:div type="orig"><p xml:id="pJ27p0052b0801">竹篦子。</p></cb:div>
<lb n="0052b09" ed="J"/><cb:div type="commentary"><p xml:id="pJ27p0052b0901" style="margin-left:1em">推位讓國，有虞陶唐，始制文字，乃服衣裳。此去三
<lb n="0052b10" ed="J"/>千里外，切忌舉著，為甚如此？不見道：雲騰致雨，露
<lb n="0052b11" ed="J"/>結為霜。</p></cb:div>
<lb n="0052b12" ed="J"/><cb:div type="orig"><p xml:id="pJ27p0052b1201">鎮州蘿蔔。</p></cb:div>
<lb n="0052b13" ed="J"/><cb:div type="commentary"><p xml:id="pJ27p0052b1301" style="margin-left:1em">鎮州蘿蔔青州棗，萬物無過出處好。爐裏煉底不
<lb n="0052b14" ed="J"/>是精金，綈箱畜者還非至寶。趙州本為定干戈，惹
<lb n="0052b15" ed="J"/>得烽煙雲嫋嫋。</p></cb:div>
<lb n="0052b16" ed="J"/><cb:div type="orig"><p xml:id="pJ27p0052b1601">雲門乾屎橛，</p></cb:div>
<lb n="0052b17" ed="J"/><cb:div type="commentary"><p xml:id="pJ27p0052b1701" style="margin-left:1em">雞冠華，當當頂上胭脂搽，秋初夏末紅滿園，卻被
<lb n="0052b18" ed="J"/>杭州城大井巷裏張媽媽家，滿頭插得向人誇，高
<lb n="0052b19" ed="J"/>聲唱云：好刷牙。</p></cb:div>
<lb n="0052b20" ed="J"/><cb:div type="orig"><p xml:id="pJ27p0052b2001">仰山明珠，</p></cb:div>
<lb n="0052b21" ed="J"/><cb:div type="commentary"><p xml:id="pJ27p0052b2101" style="margin-left:1em">師子兒善哮吼，明珠不惜當人剖。匠石斫堊兮運
<lb n="0052b22" ed="J"/>斤成風，良庖解牛兮曾未傷鋒犯手能明能暗兮
<lb n="0052b23" ed="J"/>黑月白月有擒有縱兮烏飛兔走。超群還說石崇
<lb n="0052b24" ed="J"/>家，顧指揮珍八百斗。</p></cb:div>
<lb n="0052b25" ed="J"/><cb:div type="orig"><p xml:id="pJ27p0052b2501">雪峰三相見，</p></cb:div>
<lb n="0052b26" ed="J"/><cb:div type="commentary"><p xml:id="pJ27p0052b2601" style="margin-left:1em">相逢不在望州亭，相見何曾在僧室？杖頭果若有
<lb n="0052b27" ed="J"/>餘錢，莫愁天下無相識，烏石嶺上閒雲濃。淡太華
<lb n="0052b28" ed="J"/>山頂，秋風蕭颯。南嶽天台覿面逢，高拱手兮低作
<lb n="0052b29" ed="J"/>揖。</p></cb:div>
<lb n="0052b30" ed="J"/><cb:div type="orig"><p xml:id="pJ27p0052b3001">馬祖一喝，百丈耳聾。</p></cb:div>
<pb n="0052c" ed="J" xml:id="J27.B189.0052c"/>
<lb n="0052c01" ed="J"/><cb:div type="commentary"><p xml:id="pJ27p0052c0101" style="margin-left:1em">霹靂一聲天地開。銀山銕壁<note n="0052c0101" resp="CBETA" type="add">已【CB】，巳【嘉興】</note><app n="0052c0101"><lem resp="CBETA.maha" wit="【CB】">已</lem><rdg wit="【嘉興】">巳</rdg></app>成灰。誰言毒鼓無
<lb n="0052c02" ed="J"/>消息。百丈魂褫當下薶。有機用絕安排。電光影裏
<lb n="0052c03" ed="J"/>雨華來。江西從此宗風立。法令嚴行遍九陔。</p></cb:div>
<lb n="0052c04" ed="J"/><cb:div type="orig"><p xml:id="pJ27p0052c0401">平常心是道。</p></cb:div>
<lb n="0052c05" ed="J"/><cb:div type="commentary"><p xml:id="pJ27p0052c0501" style="margin-left:1em">古今天地乾坤，來往星辰日月，寒則寒殺闍黎，熱
<lb n="0052c06" ed="J"/>則闍黎都熱。山高翠嵷，雲霄水遠。滄茫不輟，春回
<lb n="0052c07" ed="J"/>是物。生光柳絮，紛紛似雪。</p></cb:div>
<lb n="0052c08" ed="J"/><cb:div type="orig"><p xml:id="pJ27p0052c0801">雲門胡餅，</p></cb:div>
<lb n="0052c09" ed="J"/><cb:div type="commentary"><p xml:id="pJ27p0052c0901" style="margin-left:1em">聞聲無道悟，睹色無心見，一箇銕囫圇，大地成一
<lb n="0052c10" ed="J"/>片。細讀寒山詩，飽喫青州麵，觀音買胡餅，青天飛
<lb n="0052c11" ed="J"/>閃電。</p></cb:div>
<lb n="0052c12" ed="J"/><cb:div type="orig"><p xml:id="pJ27p0052c1201">龍牙二鼠侵藤，</p></cb:div>
<lb n="0052c13" ed="J"/><cb:div type="commentary"><p xml:id="pJ27p0052c1301" style="margin-left:1em">二鼠齧枯藤，渠儂善隱身，天寬覆不及，華開不遇
<lb n="0052c14" ed="J"/>春。胡僧無覓處，佛眼覷難真，龍牙機辯捷，一語見
<lb n="0052c15" ed="J"/>君臣。</p></cb:div>
<lb n="0052c16" ed="J"/><cb:div type="orig"><p xml:id="pJ27p0052c1601">審卞畣僧問佛法大意，貧兒抱子渡，恩愛競隨波。</p></cb:div>
<lb n="0052c17" ed="J"/><cb:div type="commentary"><p xml:id="pJ27p0052c1701" style="margin-left:1em">滔滔雲影共天流，切骨恩情不忍投，兩岸蘆華飛
<lb n="0052c18" ed="J"/>玉蜨，半江秋色一腔愁。</p></cb:div>
<lb n="0052c19" ed="J"/><cb:div type="orig"><p xml:id="pJ27p0052c1901">玄沙三種病人：</p></cb:div>
<lb n="0052c20" ed="J"/><cb:div type="commentary"><p xml:id="pJ27p0052c2001" style="margin-left:1em">閉門打睡艸萋萋，客到何妨三轉泥？若肯同居分
<lb n="0052c21" ed="J"/>脫粟，自家有病自家知。</p></cb:div>
<lb n="0052c22" ed="J"/><cb:div type="orig"><p xml:id="pJ27p0052c2201">鳥窠吹布毛。</p></cb:div>
<lb n="0052c23" ed="J"/><cb:div type="commentary"><p xml:id="pJ27p0052c2301" style="margin-left:1em">長林幽鳥謾嘈嘈，嫩柳臨風舞翠濤。富貴春城誰
<lb n="0052c24" ed="J"/>不愛？引人徐步上林皋。</p></cb:div>
<lb n="0052c25" ed="J"/><cb:div type="orig"><p xml:id="pJ27p0052c2501">高峰無夢想主人公。</p></cb:div>
<lb n="0052c26" ed="J"/><cb:div type="commentary"><p xml:id="pJ27p0052c2601" style="margin-left:1em">青年負俠骨，操鎚擊秦主。臣事漢高王，報韓心未
<lb n="0052c27" ed="J"/>死。定鼎戮力非臣功，挂冠辟榖歸赤松。阿呵呵！垂
<lb n="0052c28" ed="J"/>條春曉水西東，十二樓臺路路通，所愛風光只如
<lb n="0052c29" ed="J"/>此，一谿流水落華紅。</p></cb:div>
<lb n="0052c30" ed="J"/><cb:div type="orig"><p xml:id="pJ27p0052c3001">高峰枕子墮地。</p></cb:div>
<pb n="0053a" ed="J" xml:id="J27.B189.0053a"/>
<lb n="0053a01" ed="J"/><cb:div type="commentary"><p xml:id="pJ27p0053a0101" style="margin-left:1em">富春居士釣江磯，得味無如茹蕨薇，不意羊裘囊
<lb n="0053a02" ed="J"/>穎露，動他星象宿宸圍。枕子落夢初歸，月照梅花
<lb n="0053a03" ed="J"/>淚溼衣。丈夫心事誰相委？白雁數行霜夜飛。</p></cb:div>
<lb n="0053a04" ed="J"/><cb:div type="orig"><p xml:id="pJ27p0053a0401">西院兩錯。</p></cb:div>
<lb n="0053a05" ed="J"/><cb:div type="commentary"><p xml:id="pJ27p0053a0501" style="margin-left:1em">獅子反<note n="0053a0501" resp="CBETA" type="add">擲【CB】，<g ref="#CB21116"/>【嘉興】</note><app n="0053a0501"><lem resp="CBETA.maha" wit="【CB】">擲</lem><rdg wit="【嘉興】"><g ref="#CB21116"/></rdg></app>象王，迴踽孔夫子失了仁義，禮智卻是
<lb n="0053a06" ed="J"/>他自家言語羿之妻，竊得一丸靈藥，倒做了月中
<lb n="0053a07" ed="J"/>之女。瑯琊覺法華舉，匝匝清風遍寰宇，錯錯錯，不
<lb n="0053a08" ed="J"/>須提起。</p></cb:div>
<lb n="0053a09" ed="J"/><cb:div type="orig"><p xml:id="pJ27p0053a0901">深明二上座見捕魚，</p></cb:div>
<lb n="0053a10" ed="J"/><cb:div type="commentary"><p xml:id="pJ27p0053a1001" style="margin-left:1em">漁歌一拍蘆華雨，鷺鷥驚入秋煙裏。向來羇宦長
<lb n="0053a11" ed="J"/>安遊，此幸承閒步清滸。蘇公蘇公刎頸交，如何艸
<lb n="0053a12" ed="J"/>具酬知<note n="0053a1201" resp="CBETA" type="add">己【CB】，巳【嘉興】</note><app n="0053a1201"><lem resp="CBETA.maha" wit="【CB】">己</lem><rdg wit="【嘉興】">巳</rdg></app>。</p></cb:div>
<lb n="0053a13" ed="J"/><cb:div type="orig"><p xml:id="pJ27p0053a1301">香巖上樹。</p></cb:div>
<lb n="0053a14" ed="J"/><cb:div type="commentary"><p xml:id="pJ27p0053a1401" style="margin-left:1em">月色遲遲舞鶴橋，香嵒公案利吹毛。當時祇道簪
<lb n="0053a15" ed="J"/>纓美，誰識孫登一嘯高出其類，在吾曹，拈來瓦礫
<lb n="0053a16" ed="J"/>等瓊瑤。莫從樹上尋消息，聖主何曾一姓堯？</p></cb:div>
<lb n="0053a17" ed="J"/><cb:div type="orig"><p xml:id="pJ27p0053a1701">父母未生前。</p></cb:div>
<lb n="0053a18" ed="J"/><cb:div type="commentary"><p xml:id="pJ27p0053a1801" style="margin-left:1em">父母未生前，無星秤子兩頭縣，莫從傀儡尋消息。
<lb n="0053a19" ed="J"/>須知定有裏頭牽。栽五柳憶陶家，停車坐愛楓林
<lb n="0053a20" ed="J"/>晚，霜葉紅於二月華。</p></cb:div>
<lb n="0053a21" ed="J"/><cb:div type="orig"><p xml:id="pJ27p0053a2101">五位偏正<note place="inline">有序</note>。
<lb n="0053a22" ed="J"/>虛空著色，畫出劫外，真容白日挑燈，照見當時面
<lb n="0053a23" ed="J"/>目，如劫前未兆，可以墨上加煤事落，今時難辨，雪
<lb n="0053a24" ed="J"/>中有粉。故知言無其言，鼓橐籥之宮商；事無所事，
<lb n="0053a25" ed="J"/>敲秋雯之髓骨，惟證據者知之也。</p></cb:div>
<lb n="0053a26" ed="J"/><cb:div type="commentary"><p xml:id="pJ27p0053a2601" style="margin-left:1em">正中偏，秋光雪影楚江天，寒鴻不到蘆華岸，隱隱
<lb n="0053a27" ed="J"/>山河色未全。</p>
<lb n="0053a28" ed="J"/><p xml:id="pJ27p0053a2801" style="margin-left:1em">偏中正嬰兒，白髮羞窺鏡，梅華雪裏最難分，烏鴉
<lb n="0053a29" ed="J"/>點破寒光印。</p>
<lb n="0053a30" ed="J"/><p xml:id="pJ27p0053a3001" style="margin-left:1em">正中來，泥牛蹋破石蒼苔，鳥飛雖到華枝上，啼盡
<pb n="0053b" ed="J" xml:id="J27.B189.0053b"/>
<lb n="0053b01" ed="J"/>春情不染埃。</p>
<lb n="0053b02" ed="J"/><p xml:id="pJ27p0053b0201" style="margin-left:1em">兼中至，露刃交鋒撤紅幟，揮戈指日戰猶酣，劍去
<lb n="0053b03" ed="J"/>刀來善周致。</p>
<lb n="0053b04" ed="J"/><p xml:id="pJ27p0053b0401" style="margin-left:1em">兼中到，庖丁善得屠牛道，一般，鋒刃用來殊，不落
<lb n="0053b05" ed="J"/>庸情方得玅。</p>
<lb n="0053b06" ed="J"/><p xml:id="pJ27p0053b0601" style="margin-left:1em">荅即念法，姪夢話二十二問并頌：</p></cb:div>
<lb n="0053b07" ed="J"/><cb:div type="orig"><p xml:id="pJ27p0053b0701">問：如何是佛荅猢猻喫苦瓜。</p></cb:div>
<lb n="0053b08" ed="J"/><cb:div type="commentary"><p xml:id="pJ27p0053b0801" style="margin-left:1em">怨家生劫難回互，卻遇雲門恨轉賒，滿身有口難
<lb n="0053b09" ed="J"/>分說，餓久猢猻喫苦瓜。</p></cb:div>
<lb n="0053b10" ed="J"/><cb:div type="orig"><p xml:id="pJ27p0053b1001">問：如何是法荅閫外將軍令朝中天子宣。</p></cb:div>
<lb n="0053b11" ed="J"/><cb:div type="commentary"><p xml:id="pJ27p0053b1101" style="margin-left:1em">塞外將軍令最嚴，朝中誰敢悖君宣？如今海晏河
<lb n="0053b12" ed="J"/>清日，處處謳歌樂舜年。</p></cb:div>
<lb n="0053b13" ed="J"/><cb:div type="orig"><p xml:id="pJ27p0053b1301">問：如何是僧荅錫杖撥開金世界，袈裟斜搭晚來雲。</p></cb:div>
<lb n="0053b14" ed="J"/><cb:div type="commentary"><p xml:id="pJ27p0053b1401" style="margin-left:1em">錫杖撥開金世界，袈裟斜搭晚來雲，異時展缽吞
<lb n="0053b15" ed="J"/>銅汁，帶角披毛共一群。</p></cb:div>
<lb n="0053b16" ed="J"/><cb:div type="orig"><p xml:id="pJ27p0053b1601">問：如何是法身荅瞎子不眼華？</p></cb:div>
<lb n="0053b17" ed="J"/><cb:div type="commentary"><p xml:id="pJ27p0053b1701" style="margin-left:1em">瞎子從來眼不花，騎牛終日不還家，谿邊捉得烏
<lb n="0053b18" ed="J"/>龜子，產下高飛赤老鴉。</p></cb:div>
<lb n="0053b19" ed="J"/><cb:div type="orig"><p xml:id="pJ27p0053b1901">問：如何是透法身荅騎驢上火牆？</p></cb:div>
<lb n="0053b20" ed="J"/><cb:div type="commentary"><p xml:id="pJ27p0053b2001" style="margin-left:1em">騎驢上火牆，蘇武牧羝羊。昔時人<note n="0053b2001" resp="CBETA" type="add">已【CB】，巳【嘉興】</note><app n="0053b2001"><lem resp="CBETA.maha" wit="【CB】">已</lem><rdg wit="【嘉興】">巳</rdg></app>老，歸家笑一
<lb n="0053b21" ed="J"/>場，驚走新媳婦，東山水上行。</p></cb:div>
<lb n="0053b22" ed="J"/><cb:div type="orig"><p xml:id="pJ27p0053b2201">問：如何是向上事荅？今歲天多雨，米價不如常。</p></cb:div>
<lb n="0053b23" ed="J"/><cb:div type="commentary"><p xml:id="pJ27p0053b2301" style="margin-left:1em">問予向上事，老鼠喫生薑，今歲天多雨，米價不如
<lb n="0053b24" ed="J"/>常。</p></cb:div>
<lb n="0053b25" ed="J"/><cb:div type="orig"><p xml:id="pJ27p0053b2501">問：如何是向下事？荅愁殺李將軍。</p></cb:div>
<lb n="0053b26" ed="J"/><cb:div type="commentary"><p xml:id="pJ27p0053b2601" style="margin-left:1em">手拈黃葉笑殷殷，為止兒啼喚作金烽煙未息邊
<lb n="0053b27" ed="J"/>多事，一時愁殺李將軍。</p></cb:div>
<lb n="0053b28" ed="J"/><cb:div type="orig"><p xml:id="pJ27p0053b2801">問：如何是最初句？荅嚼飯餧嬰兒。</p></cb:div>
<lb n="0053b29" ed="J"/><cb:div type="commentary"><p xml:id="pJ27p0053b2901" style="margin-left:1em">少林面壁強安排，多少英雄掘地薶，識破英雄關
<lb n="0053b30" ed="J"/>捩子，何須沈醉舞三台？</p></cb:div>
<pb n="0053c" ed="J" xml:id="J27.B189.0053c"/>
<lb n="0053c01" ed="J"/><cb:div type="orig"><p xml:id="pJ27p0053c0101">問：如何是末後句？荅屋裏，販揚州。</p></cb:div>
<lb n="0053c02" ed="J"/><cb:div type="commentary"><p xml:id="pJ27p0053c0201" style="margin-left:1em">掣電之機亦強為只祈當下自知歸西施若不來
<lb n="0053c03" ed="J"/>吳國勾踐如何霸？九畿。</p></cb:div>
<lb n="0053c04" ed="J"/><cb:div type="orig"><p xml:id="pJ27p0053c0401">問：如何是道荅猛虎掛金鈴？</p></cb:div>
<lb n="0053c05" ed="J"/><cb:div type="commentary"><p xml:id="pJ27p0053c0501" style="margin-left:1em">石女秋深夜擊碪，方知枯木裏龍吟。原來祖道無
<lb n="0053c06" ed="J"/>他故，只要檀郎認得聲。</p></cb:div>
<lb n="0053c07" ed="J"/><cb:div type="orig"><p xml:id="pJ27p0053c0701">問：如何是禪荅迷人不問路？</p></cb:div>
<lb n="0053c08" ed="J"/><cb:div type="commentary"><p xml:id="pJ27p0053c0801" style="margin-left:1em">困人窗下憶鵬程，豈道詩書不誤人？相思何事關
<lb n="0053c09" ed="J"/>情急，一樹桃華幾度春。</p></cb:div>
<lb n="0053c10" ed="J"/><cb:div type="orig"><p xml:id="pJ27p0053c1001">問：如何是宗荅教書不識字？</p></cb:div>
<lb n="0053c11" ed="J"/><cb:div type="commentary"><p xml:id="pJ27p0053c1101" style="margin-left:1em">宗緒繇來立祖翁，各隨門戶顯家風，奈余邋遢居
<lb n="0053c12" ed="J"/>村里，數樹春華幾樣紅。</p></cb:div>
<lb n="0053c13" ed="J"/><cb:div type="orig"><p xml:id="pJ27p0053c1301">問：如是日用事，荅新婦下廚房。</p></cb:div>
<lb n="0053c14" ed="J"/><cb:div type="commentary"><p xml:id="pJ27p0053c1401" style="margin-left:1em">紫芋新煨午膳香，隨緣事事得尋常，泥牛從是歸
<lb n="0053c15" ed="J"/>滄海，展腳高眠折腳床。</p></cb:div>
<lb n="0053c16" ed="J"/><cb:div type="orig"><p xml:id="pJ27p0053c1601">問：如何是衲僧巴鼻荅湘江水倒流。</p></cb:div>
<lb n="0053c17" ed="J"/><cb:div type="commentary"><p xml:id="pJ27p0053c1701" style="margin-left:1em">不因吸盡西江水，那得中峰向下垂？可惜至今無
<lb n="0053c18" ed="J"/>定跡，依俙拈作雪峰蛇。</p></cb:div>
<lb n="0053c19" ed="J"/><cb:div type="orig"><p xml:id="pJ27p0053c1901">問：如何是衲僧拄杖子？荅窮漢哭家親。</p></cb:div>
<lb n="0053c20" ed="J"/><cb:div type="commentary"><p xml:id="pJ27p0053c2001" style="margin-left:1em">一條白棒，專打龍象，佛祖若來，當仁不讓。無根無
<lb n="0053c21" ed="J"/>枝，難比難況。有人問我是何宗？秋高月照梧桐上
<lb n="0053c22" ed="J"/>咄。又道難比難況復云參。</p></cb:div>
<lb n="0053c23" ed="J"/><cb:div type="orig"><p xml:id="pJ27p0053c2301">問：如何是洞上五位荅？除夜舊門神。</p></cb:div>
<lb n="0053c24" ed="J"/><cb:div type="commentary"><p xml:id="pJ27p0053c2401" style="margin-left:1em">君義臣忠父慈子孝要嫁竹夫人，土地前討笤報
<lb n="0053c25" ed="J"/>道：石幢子生來多不肖。且道侍奉一句又作麼生？
<lb n="0053c26" ed="J"/>若還借借，終不玅。</p></cb:div>
<lb n="0053c27" ed="J"/><cb:div type="orig"><p xml:id="pJ27p0053c2701">問：如何是三要荅棺材屋裏掛鍾馗？</p></cb:div>
<lb n="0053c28" ed="J"/><cb:div type="commentary"><p xml:id="pJ27p0053c2801" style="margin-left:1em">大蟲帶紙帽，驚人又好笑，老鼠打壁洞，貓兒愛鑽
<lb n="0053c29" ed="J"/>灶，為甚如此？不見道：不許夜行，投明須到。</p></cb:div>
<lb n="0053c30" ed="J"/><cb:div type="orig"><p xml:id="pJ27p0053c3001">問：如何是三玄荅啞子看西廂？</p></cb:div>
<pb n="0054a" ed="J" xml:id="J27.B189.0054a"/>
<lb n="0054a01" ed="J"/><cb:div type="commentary"><p xml:id="pJ27p0054a0101" style="margin-left:1em">第一玄月落不離天；第二玄，姜維一計害三賢；第
<lb n="0054a02" ed="J"/>三玄，繡鍼眼裏打鞦韆。第四玄自笑云：多了一玄
<lb n="0054a03" ed="J"/>了。呵呵呵關主。鬍須落半邊。</p></cb:div>
<lb n="0054a04" ed="J"/><cb:div type="orig"><p xml:id="pJ27p0054a0401">問：三玄三要，是同是別？荅閉眼食蝸牛，一場酸澀苦。</p></cb:div>
<lb n="0054a05" ed="J"/><cb:div type="commentary"><p xml:id="pJ27p0054a0501" style="margin-left:1em">若道同十箇，駝子各有宗；若道別紛紛，大雪難分
<lb n="0054a06" ed="J"/>說。癩子唱箇謊山歌，碧眼胡僧都結舌，我也似矮
<lb n="0054a07" ed="J"/>子看戲，你若笑時我眼熱。</p></cb:div>
<lb n="0054a08" ed="J"/><cb:div type="orig"><p xml:id="pJ27p0054a0801">問：如何是四料揀荅，西湖猶說林和靖？</p></cb:div>
<lb n="0054a09" ed="J"/><cb:div type="commentary"><p xml:id="pJ27p0054a0901" style="margin-left:1em">奪人不奪境，謝隱山華開，似錦奪境不奪人。汝州
<lb n="0054a10" ed="J"/>山畔楚王城，人境俱不奪，洪都江渚滕。王閣人境
<lb n="0054a11" ed="J"/>兩俱奪，塞外將軍無勳爵，祖翁立此別邪宗，等閒
<lb n="0054a12" ed="J"/>漏網成虛謔。</p></cb:div>
<lb n="0054a13" ed="J"/><cb:div type="orig"><p xml:id="pJ27p0054a1301">問：如何是四賓主荅華子拜財神？</p></cb:div>
<lb n="0054a14" ed="J"/><cb:div type="commentary"><p xml:id="pJ27p0054a1401" style="margin-left:1em">賓中賓，抱璞投人不賞音。多少夜明簾外過，頑銕
<lb n="0054a15" ed="J"/>如何點作金？</p>
<lb n="0054a16" ed="J"/><p xml:id="pJ27p0054a1601" style="margin-left:1em">賓中主，是誰能敢鋒前語？二月寒風愁殺人，宇宙
<lb n="0054a17" ed="J"/>橫行難伴侶。</p>
<lb n="0054a18" ed="J"/><p xml:id="pJ27p0054a1801" style="margin-left:1em">主中賓，秋風吹起海天雲，當鋒寶劍吹毛利，若箇
<lb n="0054a19" ed="J"/>龍門運斧斤。</p>
<lb n="0054a20" ed="J"/><p xml:id="pJ27p0054a2001" style="margin-left:1em">主中主脩羅趯倒須彌柱，四海波翻怒不休，此來
<lb n="0054a21" ed="J"/>失卻金師子。</p>
<lb n="0054a22" ed="J"/><p xml:id="pJ27p0054a2201" style="margin-left:1em">滿腔心事語人難，空向松窗耐歲寒，主主是誰相
<lb n="0054a23" ed="J"/>續得？賓賓錯認失邯鄲。主賓彷彿門庭事，賓主依
<lb n="0054a24" ed="J"/>俙悟後看。豈是強猜心意識？珠圜不撥自周盤。</p></cb:div>
<lb n="0054a25" ed="J"/><cb:div type="orig"><p xml:id="pJ27p0054a2501">問：如何是九十七圜相荅狗不咬家人？</p></cb:div>
<lb n="0054a26" ed="J"/><cb:div type="commentary"><p xml:id="pJ27p0054a2601" style="margin-left:1em">圜相有六，所謂○相，曰暗機、曰義海、曰意語、曰默
<lb n="0054a27" ed="J"/>論曰：回互咄、住住、住。恁麼說話，好似數他家寶，祖
<lb n="0054a28" ed="J"/>師門下有甚交涉？阿呵呵！且道笑箇甚麼？不見道：
<lb n="0054a29" ed="J"/>將酒酬人意不差，靈龜特地自生嗟。暗機夜奔文
<lb n="0054a30" ed="J"/>君女，義海難明鱉鼻蛇。問荅不搖三寸舌，有言何
<pb n="0054b" ed="J" xml:id="J27.B189.0054b"/>
<lb n="0054b01" ed="J"/>必五乘車？眈原遠授手，繇茲各一家。</p></cb:div>
<lb n="0054b02" ed="J"/><cb:div type="orig"><p xml:id="pJ27p0054b0201">烏石因雪峰扣門，石問：誰？峰云：鳳凰兒。石曰：作麼生？
<lb n="0054b03" ed="J"/>峰云：來啗老觀石開門搊住曰：道！道！峰擬議，石托開，
<lb n="0054b04" ed="J"/>掩卻門峰住後，示眾云：我當時入得老觀門，你這一
<lb n="0054b05" ed="J"/>隊噇酒糟漢向甚處摸索？</p></cb:div>
<lb n="0054b06" ed="J"/><cb:div type="commentary"><p xml:id="pJ27p0054b0601" style="margin-left:1em">鳳凰兒，善錐啄，烏石峰頭雲漠漠。翻騰碧浪覓金
<lb n="0054b07" ed="J"/>鱗，幾箇解尋師子躅。悔悔悔！恨不當時！下一錯。</p></cb:div>
<lb n="0054b08" ed="J"/><cb:div type="orig"><p xml:id="pJ27p0054b0801">古德喫油餈。</p></cb:div>
<lb n="0054b09" ed="J"/><cb:div type="commentary"><p xml:id="pJ27p0054b0901" style="margin-left:1em">日上扶桑遍界暉，竹林新汲啟柴扉。問津小艇偏
<lb n="0054b10" ed="J"/>多語，逗得郎君笑眼微。</p>
<lb n="0054b11" ed="J"/><p xml:id="pJ27p0054b1101" style="margin-left:1em">頭上花枝照酒卮酒，卮中有好花枝身輕與世太
<lb n="0054b12" ed="J"/>平日眼見六朝全盛時。</p></cb:div></cb:div>
</body></text></TEI>